view.interfaces

Interface GameEngineCallbackSupport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GameEngineCallbackGUISupport

    public interface GameEngineCallbackSupport
    Interface for the class that aids the GameEngineCallback. Provides additional functionality for logging of events in the GameEngine.
